name: Trenchfire
overview: Released as part of COMPUTE!'s Gazette 1984/03 (Issue #09), 64'er Spielesammlung #5 as Ultrasonic it was released in Commodore Computer Club N°02. as Death Trench it was released in 75 Spill Datatronic, as Starfighter it was released in game of "The Big 100" collection, and as a part of the "Star Fighter" game pack. A trench shooter based on the trench sections of the Star Wars arcade game.
